                        <p class="note" MadCap:autonum="&lt;b&gt;Note: &lt;/b&gt;">This check applies only to model-based <MadCap:variable name="General.changelog" />s such as XML, YAML, and JSON. It does not apply to SQL&#160;<MadCap:variable name="General.changelog" />s.</p>
